high_descs: Turn left and move towards the brown coffee maker to the right of the sink and above the dishwasher.
Open the right cabinet door above the coffee maker, pick up the gray plate, then close the cabinet door.
Turn left and move to the white range to the right of the gray toaster.
Open the red microwave above the range, place the plate in the microwave, microwave the plate, then open the microwave, pick up the plate, and then close the microwave door.
Move slightly left to the counter area between the wall and the range.
Place the gray plate on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated plate on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the counter, then turn left and walk up to the coffee machine and look up at the upper cabinets.
Open the right upper cabinet door and take the grey plate out of the cabinet, then close the door.
Walk over to the stove on your left and look up at the microwave.
Heat up the grey plate in the microwave for a couple seconds then take it out and close the microwave.
Turn left and walk up to the wall, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the heated grey plate on the counter to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated grey plate on the counter.

high_descs: turn left and walk to the end of the kitchen counter then turn left to face the cabinet above the coffee maker
grab the plate out of the top right cabinet
turn left and walk over to the stove on the right up ahead
place the plate inside the microwave above the stove, microwave it, then take it back out
move to the left a bit and face the stove again
place the plate down on the kitchen counter to the left of the stove
anns.task_desc: place a microwaved plate down on the kitchen counter
